Student Information System for the imaginary University of Knowit

* Program calculates the weighted average grade of students
- Class Student(variable int[] grades)
- weighted average grade calculator

***Grades weight equals how many times it occurs in grade list

*** Data points may contribute equally to the final average
***add weight*grade divided with number of grades (equal weight)
 
* The student list needs to be sorted by their weighted average grade

** If the weighted average grade is equal on two or more students then they need to be sorted by their names
- CustomComparator

* The grades need to be read in from an XML file format
- StudentReader
''' weight set in xml

* Graphical user interface
- List of students and their weighted average grades


